rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Until recently, I thought
this place was fine if you
just got used to it, but...

rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0002
rows.name:
The hideout for the anti-imperial
organization Brionac was right
below here, wasn't it?

rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0003
rows.name:
No wonder pure Superbians look
at this place with pity, saying
it's a dangerous area.

rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0004
rows.name:
I didn't know much about
Brionac until now.

rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0005
rows.name:
But as long as I'm living in the
Superbian Empire, I really need to
be more aware of these things.
